metadata.name: One-Year Anniversary
metadata.description: Masterbrews celebrates our first year in business - and we want YOU to come celebrate with us! Join us on March 28th, starting at 4PM UTC as we host a day full of surprises, special guests (Twitter Spaces), giveaways, prizes, Discord games, and more! Join us in our brand-new Discord at: discord.gg/masterbrews and feel free to bring your friends. The more, the merrier!
